    ##  Settings for the shape type of the die pads. 
    ## <list type="table"> 
    ## <listheader><term> 
    ## Enumerator</term><description> 
    ## Comment</description> </listheader><item><term> 
    ## Rectangular</term><description> 
    ##  Rectangular pad. </description> </item><item><term> 
    ## Circular</term><description> 
    ##  Circular pad. </description> </item><item><term> 
    ## Curve</term><description> 
    ##  Curve defined pad. </description> </item></list>
